name: Lola Tash
introduction: Lola Bridgette Tash is a Canadian actress.Famous for her roles as Gisela Calicos and Sloan Daniels on the respective television series Connor Undercover and Republic of Doyle, Tash is also notable for her performances in the movies After the Ball (as Polly) and Molly Maxwell (as the title character).Early in her acting career, she appeared in episodes of Rookie Blue and The Latest Buzz.
